%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^DEITIES%^RESET%^

The world of ShadowGate is pantheistic, it includes the next deities

%^CYAN%^Kismet: Magic/Knowledge
  %^CYAN%^Domains :%^CYAN%^%^CYAN%^ creation, knowledge, law, magic, mentalism, stars
  %^CYAN%^Enemies :%^CYAN%^%^CYAN%^ none
%^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^Lysara: Death/Fate
  %^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^Domains :%^MAGENTA%^ fate, moon, repose, travel, void, water
  %^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^Enemies :%^MAGENTA%^ Nilith, Lord Shadow
%^GREEN%^Nimnavanon: Forests/Weather
  %^GREEN%^Domains :%^GREEN%^%^GREEN%^ animal, destruction, earth, plant, storms
  %^GREEN%^Enemies :%^GREEN%^%^GREEN%^ Nilith
%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Jarmila: Light/Love
  %^BOLD%^%^RED%^Domains :%^RED%^ fire, good, protection, renewal, sun
  %^BOLD%^%^RED%^Enemies : Lord Shadow, Nilith, The Faceless One
%^BOLD%^Kreysneothosies: Home/Protection
  %^BOLD%^Domains : earth, law, protection, strength, vigilance
  %^BOLD%^Enemies : The Faceless One, Nilith
%^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Callamir: Luck/Trickery
  %^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Domains :%^BLUE%^ air, chaos, charm, good, travel, trickery
  %^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Enemies :%^BLUE%^ The Faceless One, Lord Shadow
%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Lord Shadow: Darkness/Tyranny
  %^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Domains :%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^ cold, darkness, evil, law, suffering, tyranny
  %^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Enemies :%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^ Jarmila, Callamir, Lysara
%^ORANGE%^Nilith: Undeath/War
  %^ORANGE%^Domains :%^ORANGE%^%^ORANGE%^ chaos, destruction, evil, strength, war
  %^ORANGE%^Enemies :%^ORANGE%^%^ORANGE%^ Lysara, Kreysneothosies, Jarmila, Nimnavanon
%^RED%^The Faceless One: Murder/Deception
  %^RED%^Domains :%^RED%^ cavern, darkness, evil, illusion, madness, trickery
  %^RED%^Enemies :%^RED%^ Jarmila, Callamir, Kreysneothosies
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Ryorik: Elements/Natural Disasters
  %^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Domains :%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^ none
  %^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Enemies :%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^ none

You can choose to follow a god if your alignment is within two steps on the grid of deity's alignment, if you're a cleric that restriction increases to just one step.

%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^domains, individual help files for each deity, alignments
